  "subject": "Add batch event producer with exactly-once semantics",
  "commit_message": "Add batch event producer with exactly-once semantics\n\n\t- Renamed Kafka config to ExactlyOnceSemanticsKafkaConfi\n\t- Refactored all shortcuts 'EOS' to full name as previous patch\n\t  comment (https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/cps/+/143361)\n\t- Added EventBatchSendException for batch error handling\n\t- Added method in EventProducer for batch send\n\t- Added unit tests for above changes\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-3162\nChange-Id: Ia818e8bf342ac212b365f7c24038ee285acd3f24\nSigned-off-by: emaclee <lee.anjella.macabuhay@est.tech>\n",
